buyerAgent.name: The Stephen Cooley Real Estate Group

data.description:
Welcome to your dream home nestled in the serene surroundings of Clover and Lake Wylie! This stunning 3 BR, 2 bath home boasts luxurious features and a prime location for those seeking both comfort and convenience. Prepare delicious meals in the open kitchen-complete with a giant island; perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying family meals. Enjoy the abundance of natural light that floods the open living area.
All 3 bedrooms offer ample space for relaxation & privacy. Two full bathrooms feature sleek fixtures & contemporary finishes. Primary suite includes dual sinks & huge walk-in closet!
Enjoy the beauty of laminate hardwood flooring throughout the home-offering the look of real hardwood with added durability and easy maintenance. Step outside to the screened porch & adjoining patio overlooking the large fenced back yard.

Enjoy easy access to neighborhood pools, the clubhouse, & a scenic walking trail to explore the natural beauty of the community. Schedule a showing today!
